preference.name: Baseline_part_update_required_dstypes
preference.preference_description: Specifies the list of the ONLY dataset types which would force a part update to be performed for the Item types that are not listed by Baseline_part_update_not_required_item_types. E.g. Baseline_part_update_required_dstypes=UGMASTER,UGPART. NOTE: This is valid only when the Baseline_nxmanager_part_update is set to 1.
